Elizabeth I is a docu-drama series about the life of Queen Elizabeth 1, with commentary by expert presenters Susannah Lipscomb and Dan Jones. 

Season 1, Episode 1 – “Battle for the Throne” 
This episode charts her turbulent early years from age three when her mother was executed and she was declared illegitimate and banished from court, through the dangers she faced due to the machinations of Thomas Seymour and the hatred of her half-sister Mary, to the start of her reign
